ZH: 我们今天晚上要吃火锅。
EN: We are going to have hot pot for dinner tonight.

ZH: 火锅里有各种各样的食材。
EN: There are all kinds of ingredients in hot pot.

ZH: 我喜欢在火锅里加辣椒。
EN: I like to add chili peppers in my hot pot.

ZH: 火锅是我最喜欢的中餐之一。
EN: Hot pot is one of my favorite Chinese dishes.

ZH: 在冬天吃火锅真是最舒服的事情。
EN: Having hot pot in winter is the most comforting thing.

ZH: 你想要吃牛肉还是羊肉火锅？
EN: Do you want to have beef hot pot or lamb hot pot?

ZH: 火锅店里的火锅底料非常美味。
EN: The hot pot base in hot pot restaurants is delicious.

ZH: 老板，再来一份蔬菜火锅底料。
EN: Boss, another order of vegetable hot pot base, please.

ZH: 火锅吃到最后的时候，面条最好吃了。
EN: Noodles are the best when eating hot pot towards the end.

ZH: 每次见朋友都会选火锅吃。
EN: I always choose hot pot when meeting friends.

ZH: 火锅能让人们聚在一起吃饭。
EN: Hot pot brings people together for a meal.

ZH: 在家吃火锅可以省下很多钱。
EN: Eating hot pot at home can save a lot of money.

ZH: 小孩子们都很喜欢吃火锅。
EN: Kids all love eating hot pot.

ZH: 火锅餐厅的环境非常好。
EN: The atmosphere in hot pot restaurants is very nice.

ZH: 火锅里的肉片一下就熟了。
EN: The meat slices in hot pot cook quickly.

ZH: 火锅配上啤酒最开心了。
EN: Hot pot with beer is the happiest combination.

ZH: 火锅的味道犹如家的温暖。
EN: The taste of hot pot is like the warmth of home.

ZH: 我们那里有一家火锅店开了很多年了。
EN: There is a hot pot restaurant that has been open for many years in our area.

ZH: 火锅店的服务员都很友好。
EN: The waiters at the hot pot restaurant are very friendly.
